summary: The final showdown with Thanos should have been between Thor, Carol, and Wanda as the arguably most powerful Avengers. Like I...
body: The final showdown with Thanos should have been between Thor, Carol, and Wanda as the arguably most powerful Avengers. Like I GET that they wanted to conclude these big arcs for Tony and Steve given that their runs are now done, but COME ON. The movie should have been just as much about setting up the the newer people as the New Avengers it was about concluding the arcs of the old ones.
